    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price, provided they are comfortable with some cosmetic imperfections and upcoming maintenance needs.",
      "price": 20000.0,
